\Rightarrow \frac{4x-12}{x^2+2x+1-16}
\Rightarrow \frac{4x-12}{(x+1)^2-16}
\Rightarrow \frac{4x-12}{\enclose{circle}[mathcolor="Red"]{\underline{ (x+5)(x-3)}}}$. Now, $4x-12$ is divisible by $x-3$
\end think <answer> $2$ </answer>

